<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我找你<delay8 />找了好久咧！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有個東西想交給你<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你猜是什麼呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />鏘鏘～！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是可以點綴季節的<colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聖誕節花圈<colour id="65535" />喔。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個很適合<delay8 />拿來裝飾家門對吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我們把家門好好裝飾一番，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以迎接聖誕節吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay40 />你的包包是不是<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />塞滿了一堆東西啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣<delay8 />我沒辦法把東西交給你呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這東西就先由我來保管。<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好意思，<delay8 />能請你整理好包包後
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再來我這裡一趟嗎？<delay40 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />萬事拜託囉，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>